very stubborn.

552
00:29:08,485 --> 00:29:11,165
She never cares if the whole world
thinks she's wrong.

553
00:29:12,445 --> 00:29:13,925
She's still going to persevere.

554
00:29:16,165 --> 00:29:17,885
Whenever we spend time together,

555
00:29:19,765 --> 00:29:22,685
I feel very comfortable and relaxed.

556
00:29:23,285 --> 00:29:26,045
I can just be myself without feeling
the burden of being an idol.

557
00:29:26,125 --> 00:29:27,285
Later on,

558
00:29:28,765 --> 00:29:30,125
gradually, I realized that

559
00:29:31,605 --> 00:29:32,845
unknowingly, I began

560
00:29:32,925 --> 00:29:34,605
to take notice on everything she does.

561
00:29:35,365 --> 00:29:37,165
I keep on looking for her.

562
00:29:39,005 --> 00:29:41,405
Whenever she interacts with other guys,

563
00:29:42,565 --> 00:29:44,565
I would feel frustrated,

564
00:29:45,325 --> 00:29:48,565
 lousy and throw a tantrum at her.

565
00:29:49,885 --> 00:29:51,125
Until one day,

566
00:29:52,445 --> 00:29:54,125
I saw she was wrongly accused.

567
00:29:54,725 --> 00:29:55,805
Then I knew

568
00:29:56,525 --> 00:29:57,765
Chen Qingqing

569
00:29:58,485 --> 00:29:59,805
is just like any other girl.

570
00:30:00,365 --> 00:30:01,965
She too needs to be loved and cared for.

571
00:30:04,245 --> 00:30:06,125
From that moment,

572
00:30:06,685 --> 00:30:07,805
I was certain

573
00:30:08,365 --> 00:30:11,085
that I have fallen for her.

574
00:30:11,765 --> 00:30:15,925
I have fallen deeply for her.

575
00:30:18,765 --> 00:30:19,965
I want to hold her in my arms

576
00:30:21,845 --> 00:30:22,845
and protect her

577
00:30:25,325 --> 00:30:26,165
even if

578
00:30:27,205 --> 00:30:28,845
the world is against me.

579
00:30:40,445 --> 00:30:42,605
Qingchen, look!

580
00:30:42,805 --> 00:30:44,125
It's the meteor shower!

581
00:30:48,685 --> 00:30:50,485
If Chen Qingqing was here,

582
00:30:51,605 --> 00:30:52,605
it would be perfect.

583
00:30:56,845 --> 00:30:57,925
Let's make a wish.

584
00:31:00,725 --> 00:31:01,565
Okay.

585
00:31:14,285 --> 00:31:16,765
Qingqing, don't tell me

586
00:31:17,005 --> 00:31:18,845
