588
00:31:32,485 --> 00:31:33,805
Did she find out
what happened at the cave?

589
00:31:33,885 --> 00:31:36,245
She seemed furious
whenever I mentioned Qingchen.

590
00:31:37,165 --> 00:31:38,485
Where's Qingqing?

591
00:31:38,565 --> 00:31:40,365
