not to go see her.

592
00:31:40,765 --> 00:31:41,605
Excuse me.

593
00:31:41,725 --> 00:31:42,925
Stop running, you pervert!

594
00:31:43,005 --> 00:31:44,205
We need to catch this pervert!

595
00:31:44,285 --> 00:31:47,325
The reason you came to this college
was because of your dad, wasn't it?

596
00:31:47,405 --> 00:31:49,765
So it was all a lie.

597
00:31:49,845 --> 00:31:51,165
Liar!

598
00:31:51,245 --> 00:31:53,605
If you ever need help,
you should come and look for me.

599
00:31:53,685 --> 00:31:55,725
-Happy Birthday, Qingqing!
-Happy Birthday!

